data.description: Built in 2020, Super popular Sweetgum floor plan no longer offered by Beazer Homes in Jasmine Point! 4Br 3.5Bth 3000sq ft home with in-law suite! 9' ceiling heights throughout, Light and bright througout the home. Walk in to your wide entry hall with Office with french doors on your right! Perfect for working from home! Enter into the main space of the home, with Great entertaining spaces, Large White Kitchen with Quartz Countertops and tiled backsplash! Large Island with plenty of storage, Open space looking into the Living room with great fireplace! Master on the main with awesome bathroom with large walk in closet!  Upstairs has a huge 19'x19' loft space perfect for the kids, 3 more Bedrooms on the second floor with 2 full baths! Granite countertops in all the Bathrooms upstairs. Community Pool and Pavilion and protected wetlands around the community, Great walking trails and close to everything! Come by Today! Additional Pictures Coming!
